{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"1. **`internal/agent/runner.go`** - When the engine returns an error, the agent now extracts the failed step name from `run.StepExecutions` (looking for steps with \"error\" or \"fail\" result) and includes it in the `MsgError` status message sent to the daemon.","timestamp":"2026-03-13T19:49:55.599312276Z"}
