{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"   - Uses the captured error message when finalizing failed runs: calls `run.Fail(reportedError)` instead of `run.Complete(RunStateFailed)`, which sets the `ErrorMessage` field on the run","timestamp":"2026-03-13T19:49:55.599335921Z"}
